author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Voya Financial To Acquire Pen-Cal Administrators

organizations.name: brief-voya financial to acquire pen-cal administrators voya financial inc

text:
Voya Financial Inc:
* VOYA FINANCIAL TO ACQUIRE PEN-CAL ADMINISTRATORS
* VOYA FINANCIAL INC - TERMS OF TRANSACTION WERE NOT DISCLOSED, AND ARE NOT MATERIAL TO VOYA’S FINANCIAL POSITION.
* VOYA FINANCIAL INC - TERMS OF TRANSACTION WERE NOT DISCLOSED
* VOYA FINANCIAL INC - PEN-CAL WILL BECOME PART OF VOYA’S RETIREMENT BUSINESS OPERATING UNIT
* VOYA FINANCIAL INC - AS PART OF DEAL, PEN-CAL WILL RE-BRAND TO VOYA Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
